WITH selected_rows AS MATERIALIZED (
    SELECT 
        sample_id,
        array_sort(array_slice(
            array_agg(customer.rowid ORDER BY RANDOM()),
            1,
            (SELECT COUNT(*) / 2 FROM customer)
        )) AS row_ids
    FROM 
        range(1024) AS t(sample_id)
    CROSS JOIN
        customer
    GROUP BY 
        sample_id
    ORDER BY 
        sample_id
)
SELECT
    sample_id,
    array(
        SELECT 
            CASE 
                WHEN customer.rowid IN (
                    SELECT unnest(row_ids)
                    FROM selected_rows
                    WHERE sample_id = sr.sample_id
                ) THEN TRUE 
                ELSE FALSE 
            END
        FROM 
            customer
    ) AS mask
FROM
    selected_rows AS sr
GROUP BY
    sample_id
ORDER BY
    sample_id;
